{"tid":149324,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星會長疑召妓 指使偷拍者被捕","createTime":"2017-03-09T08:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T08:29:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a780b4ad7cc24942c840d6d76f6bd100e7fb4b","tid":149324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:17:24.000Z","msg":"【本報綜合報道】南韓三星集團會長李健熙去年被指於二○一一年至一三年間，多次在首爾家中召妓，有當地傳媒更公開短片，顯示一名疑似李健熙的男子與一名女子暗示性交易的對話。南韓首爾中央地方檢察院周二表示，上月拘捕了一名男子，懷疑他指使片中女子偷拍該段影片，用以勒索三星集團。檢方亦會調查李健熙是否參與嫖妓。<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170309/photo/0309-00180-017v1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170309%2Fphoto%2F0309-00180-017v1.jpg&h=9210e566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n檢察院指出，他們於上月廿五日以涉嫌違反「懲治性罪案特殊法案」的罪名拘捕一名男子，現正調查疑犯有否指使片中女子進行偷拍，作勒索三星之用。該男子被指是南韓大型企業CJ集團一間子公司的前職員，相信是單獨行事。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，疑犯曾在CJ集團一間子公司內，在主要管理部門內任職行政人員，CJ集團於三月三日已接受疑犯的請辭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170309/00180_017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170309%2F00180_017.html&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9opZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8617b9fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170309/00180_017.html</a>"},{"pid":"50f0ee7ae42d2cf3b4704142aa8293e3ece45d5c","tid":149324,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"會長洗自己落去叫雞嫁咩"},{"pid":"30785b744eef3e600ccede8b939b630e95f6b218","tid":149324,"uid":4896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"韓國call g犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231a73b8b55e7b4d3a79a586219152aa6165a60a","tid":149324,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"有錢佬叫雞好難食散餐<br />\n<br />\n一食就要包女明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=